Dialogue: 11,0:00:49.97,0:00:55.14,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}This “vision” we call life
Dialogue: 11,0:00:55.14,0:01:01.19,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Is yet unaware that it’s an illusion
Dialogue: 11,0:01:02.11,0:01:07.57,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Even antinomic paradoxes
Dialogue: 11,0:01:07.57,0:01:13.00,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Can be tricked into existence by an infinite amount of world lines
Dialogue: 11,0:01:13.00,0:01:18.33,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}If the natural trajectory dictated by emotional decisions
Dialogue: 11,0:01:18.33,0:01:22.67,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Supersedes even common sense
Dialogue: 11,0:01:22.67,0:01:28.05,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Then my—and merely my—
Dialogue: 11,0:01:28.05,0:01:34.77,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Suffering, and my mistakes, will still neatly follow the algorithm
Dialogue: 11,0:01:35.89,0:01:41.19,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Words and tokens of love—memories growing ever stronger
Dialogue: 11,0:01:41.77,0:01:46.65,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Guarantee I will not leave you behind a second time
Dialogue: 11,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.37,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}I am forever by your side
Dialogue: 11,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.08,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}We’re joined together as one
Dialogue: 11,0:01:52.08,0:01:57.54,OP Trans,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.25\fad(100,100)}Out of this quantum entanglement, “0” will manifest
Dialogue: 11,0:20:09.05,0:20:13.14,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Orihime-sama niwa narenai
Dialogue: 11,0:20:14.89,0:20:21.64,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Watashi no chikara ja sasaekirenai kedo
Dialogue: 11,0:20:21.64,0:20:26.61,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Hanarebanare ga kowakute
Dialogue: 11,0:20:26.61,0:20:31.11,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Oinori wo suru yo
Dialogue: 11,0:20:31.11,0:20:35.57,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Soremo ai nano kana?
Dialogue: 11,0:20:35.57,0:20:41.08,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Subete no, bamen ga koishisugite
Dialogue: 11,0:20:41.08,0:20:46.59,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Bokura wa mata ano basho he to
Dialogue: 11,0:20:46.59,0:20:53.01,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Donna mabushii hikari no sekaisen mo
Dialogue: 11,0:20:53.01,0:20:59.31,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Kanashimi toka yorokobi wakare mo atte
Dialogue: 11,0:20:59.31,0:21:05.77,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Naita mama de anata no hoho wo tataku
Dialogue: 11,0:21:05.77,0:21:12.86,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Sono shunkan nanika ga kawaru yo
Dialogue: 11,0:21:12.86,0:21:19.20,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Me niwa utsuranai mamoru beki nanika he
Dialogue: 11,0:21:19.20,0:21:30.67,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Inochi sae sasagu sore ga minna no sentaku
Dialogue: 11,0:21:34.55,0:21:41.22,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Ooinaru umi watatte
Dialogue: 11,0:21:41.22,0:21:46.85,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Tsuginaru taisetsu na bunkiten
Dialogue: 11,0:21:46.85,0:21:55.49,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Atarashii mirai no monogatari no shujinkou he
Dialogue: 11,0:21:55.49,0:22:02.91,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Itsuka aeru ne sono hi made
Dialogue: 11,0:22:27.39,0:22:33.78,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Kirameku hoshi yozora ni te wo nobaseba
Dialogue: 11,0:22:33.78,0:22:40.20,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Yomigaeru ne omoi mo nukumori no hi mo
Dialogue: 11,0:22:40.20,0:22:46.50,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\fs90}Afuredasu yo ano toki ano bamen de
Dialogue: 11,0:22:46.50,0:22:53.63,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\fs90}Kimi no kotoba naitewaratta
Dialogue: 11,0:22:53.63,0:22:59.97,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\fs90}Kioku no subete ga kakikawaru toshitemo
Dialogue: 11,0:22:59.97,0:23:13.36,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\fs90}Dejabu mitai ni kokoro no oku de yureteru
Dialogue: 11,0:20:09.05,0:20:13.14,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I still can’t become your Orihime
Dialogue: 11,0:20:14.89,0:20:21.64,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I don’t have the strength to support you, but even so
Dialogue: 11,0:20:21.64,0:20:26.61,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I’m terrified of losing you for good
Dialogue: 11,0:20:26.61,0:20:31.11,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}So I’ll pray for your happiness
Dialogue: 11,0:20:31.11,0:20:35.57,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Isn’t that also a form of love?
Dialogue: 11,0:20:35.57,0:20:41.08,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I long for all the scenes, back in those days
Dialogue: 11,0:20:41.08,0:20:46.59,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}And so we head once again toward that place...
Dialogue: 11,0:20:46.59,0:20:53.01,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}In that world line, shining with the most radiant light
Dialogue: 11,0:20:53.01,0:20:59.31,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Where you said your most bittersweet farewell
Dialogue: 11,0:20:59.31,0:21:05.77,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I will strike your cheek, crying all the while
Dialogue: 11,0:21:05.77,0:21:12.86,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Changing everything in that moment
Dialogue: 11,0:21:12.86,0:21:19.20,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}To protect your vision not yet reflected in our eyes
Dialogue: 11,0:21:19.20,0:21:30.67,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}We will dedicate our lives—that is the choice of all of us
Dialogue: 11,0:21:34.55,0:21:41.22,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}We will cross the vast ocean
Dialogue: 11,0:21:41.22,0:21:46.85,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Toward the next important divergence point
Dialogue: 11,0:21:46.85,0:21:55.49,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}So that someday, in a new future
Dialogue: 11,0:21:55.49,0:22:02.91,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}I can meet the protagonist of that story, but until then...
Dialogue: 11,0:22:27.39,0:22:33.78,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Whenever I stretch my hand out toward the sparkling stars in the night sky
Dialogue: 11,0:22:33.78,0:22:40.20,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}Feelings and warm moments reawaken within me
Dialogue: 11,0:22:40.20,0:22:46.50,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\an2\fs90}Memories of those times, of those scenes, all come flooding back
Dialogue: 11,0:22:46.50,0:22:53.63,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\an2\fs90}All the words you spoke to me, all the times we laughed and cried
Dialogue: 11,0:22:53.63,0:22:59.97,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\an2\fs90}Even if all our memories are rewritten,
Dialogue: 11,0:22:59.97,0:23:13.36,Lyra Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\an2\fs90}They’ll still waver deep within our hearts as déjà vu
