Dialogue: 30,0:00:07.09,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t panic. The world line hasn’t changed.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:10.42,0:00:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, Mayuri and Suzuha are okay.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This can’t be where they...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Lintahlo.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:29.94,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Leskinen?
Dialogue: 30,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Mayu!
Dialogue: 30,0:02:14.84,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Reyes?
Dialogue: 30,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do... to Mommy?
Dialogue: 30,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Open Fire!
Dialogue: 30,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t be afraid!
Dialogue: 30,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the body! Slow down her movements!
Dialogue: 30,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious how it’s going up there on the roof?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:21.20,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not good manners to answer\Na question with a question, Lintahlo.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll dock your grades.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:27.74,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, to think you’d\Nshow up here so quickly...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:32.37,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it? Who gave you the big hint?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:37.55,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho? No... I suppose\Nif it’s anyone, it’s [Kurisu].
Dialogue: 30,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kurisu]?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Father and God...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:46.22,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To Amadeus, the professor who created\Nthe system is both father and God...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she really say something like that?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:58.44,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel kinda slick, for her\Nto praise me as a God like that.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But, she also had this to say...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our most secret domains were unveiled,
Dialogue: 30,0:04:08.87,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so we may tell Father the secrets of\Nmanipulating time and where they’re at.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So dim, Lintahlo.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:15.50,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you got a message saying all that,\Nyou should know the answer already.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:21.80,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m afraid to say you’re in too deep.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A scientist.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:31.18,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, science isn’t\Nalways a charity, you know?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you’ve heard of\Nthe company Strategic Focus?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Strat... You mean Stratfoc?!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:42.90,0:04:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a private intelligence agency called\Na shadow CIA, among other things.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you... from the very beginning!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,America, Russia...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:52.58,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All the great powers escalate the conflict\Nto obtain a time machine starting this very day.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:59.63,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t exactly act before that point\Nbecause everything was to converge.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:05.55,0:05:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve been itching with excitement\Nfor this day to finally come.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:10.35,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it you know\Nwhat I’m getting at, Lintahlo.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he know all that?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:19.48,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Hiyajo-san? Don’t tell me she...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it can’t be...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:23.90,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu’s memories in Amadeus are\Nall from before she came to Japan.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who could have...?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:32.04,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The look on your face says you’re dying\Nto know how I possibly knew all that.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s someone, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:38.54,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One who knows everything,\Nbeing a little messenger from the future...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari?!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Mayu.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:50.51,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:53.81,0:05:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still. That ricochet had to have\Ngrazed you, but you’re still bleeding.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t look!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...to Mommy?!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:33.81,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they still at it? And here\NI told her to avoid making a fuss...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:50.86,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t, Big Sis Mayu!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, this isn’t...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:26.19,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was... because Mommy...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:33.16,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy... I’m sorry, Mommy.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How’s Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Her head is a bit cut up, but she’s fine.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No other injuries.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... Mayuri’s okay.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t try to talk.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:04.02,0:08:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, don’t worry about me.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:07.82,0:08:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, even though I’m like this,\NI don’t feel the pain at all...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t try to be tough. Just—
Dialogue: 30,0:08:14.74,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the voice of God...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:18.03,0:08:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling me it doesn’t hurt...\NTelling me not to suffer...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why... this doesn’t...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari... Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:31.80,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu-san.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-chan.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy? Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Suzuha...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:46.94,0:08:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I hear the voice of God,\Neverything in my head gets messed up.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:52.94,0:08:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,God tells me... what I must do... and I do it.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:58.78,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m... sorry...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,—Kagari-chan!\N—Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I missed the big party.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:09.79,0:09:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The future’s brainwashing and enhancement\Ntechniques sure are incredible.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You did this... to Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was more of a joint effort.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:21.51,0:09:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,By me... and well, me.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know what exactly\Nyou’re getting at, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all your fault this happened to Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I said you’re right?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good on you for stopping.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha, I’m sorry...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:59.47,0:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho, isn’t this crazy? Hard to believe, I know.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:03.56,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this was all destined\Nto happen ahead of time.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Destined to happen?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:10.19,0:10:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Observation and insight\Nis what sets scientists apart.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:14.28,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you hear what I said?\NThis is a joint effort between me and myself.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Spanning across time.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Time?!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It can’t be!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:24.45,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,13 years ago, when for the\Nvery first time Kagari approached me,
Dialogue: 30,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,can you guess what she said?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:36.38,0:10:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the voice of God.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,God?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:41.09,0:10:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The future you... is calling me.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The future... Professor?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right. Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:02.03,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Me in the future sent Kagari back into the past.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:06.70,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All so I could obtain\Nthe power of manipulating time.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:10.62,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The future you did?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Kagari was...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And what an intricate plan it was.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:17.13,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to track the movements of the\Nresistance you form in the distant future...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:22.39,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...I trained countless young girls\Nand boys to act as spies and infiltrate in.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:27.64,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re all so softhearted,\Nyou fell right for the bait.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:33.15,0:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But see, then came the pinnacle of my plan.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:37.07,0:11:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If somehow or another,\Nyou managed to escape to the past...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:41.49,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure to send along a messenger\Nto my past self... using brainwashing.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hardly believe it myself.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:55.21,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But the more and more I researched,\NI began to realize her story checked out.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:01.34,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I concluded the time machine was real\Nand that Kagari actually came from the future.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:07.39,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, did you make Amadeus because...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:10.85,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. Because Kurisu goes and dies.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed a system that preserved\Nher precious time machine theory
Dialogue: 30,0:12:18.40,0:12:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and all those memories of hers.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:21.15,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! That’s what you did it for?!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:23.99,0:12:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You basically let Kurisu die?! Professor!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:27.99,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I did was long, tiresome groundwork\Nto come steal the time machine today.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:34.87,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Defy causality, overcome convergence...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the grand plan of my future self,
Dialogue: 30,0:12:40.46,0:12:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,all so I can shape the\Nways of this world on my own.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You would go that far?!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:48.05,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you obtained the time machine,\Nwhat were you planning to do?!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:52.10,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lintahlo... You fail to grasp\Nthe essence of science.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about scientists...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We experiment in hopes\Nthat our theories prove true,
Dialogue: 30,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and observing just that is what we live for.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:06.66,0:13:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The future me has such a theory\Nand the past me will set out to prove it.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:11.87,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s all it is. It’s what I always do.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll make a time paradox!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:17.50,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you afraid of breaking\Nthe world beyond repair?!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:21.05,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If that sort of thing does happen,\NI’d like to see it for myself.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:31.76,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if she’s dead, all that future\Nbrainwashing doesn’t help all too much.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:41.69,0:13:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re a true mad scientist!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:48.66,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn’t ask for a better\Ncompliment than that, Lintahlo!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you step out of my way now?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This place will be a battlefield before long.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:04.96,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With this time machine at the center of it all.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Battlefield?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s Dr. Nakabachi’s paper\Nwho defected to Russia.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:13.47,0:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, there’s the info regarding the\Ntime machine I handed over to Stratfoc.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:19.06,0:14:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That information war evolves into both sides\Nshowing up in force this very day, of all days.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,History says the\Ntime machine is destroyed here.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:28.95,0:14:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn’t exist for another 25 years\Nwhen it’s developed based on the theory.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, what if someone\Nstole it at the perfect time?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:39.42,0:14:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they fake its destruction\Nand went into the past?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what your plan is?!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s been 10 odd years since meeting Kagari.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a long time...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:53.10,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,—I’ve come so far, but it’s time—\N—I hear...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...the voice of God.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off me.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s too early to get knocked out!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:26.75,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari suffered a\Nthousand times worse than this!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Way worse! Way worse!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,—She hurt way worse than this!\N—Stop it, Suzuha!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:34.18,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up! You damn... You damn...!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Don’t stop me!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s enough, Suzuha.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:49.49,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill the guy, you’re the same as him.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-chan...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-chan!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-chan? Look, it’s Suzu-san.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:21.64,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the same hand that...\Nheld mine when... I was... scared.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So warm...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:32.40,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Big Sis Suzuha...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:41.12,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari... Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it come to this?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 30,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay! She’s not hurt!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the professor!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu-san, let’s go!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The time machine will be destroyed soon, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:27.04,0:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go before that!\NGo, and change the future!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that DURPA?!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For Kagari-chan too!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you’ve got to do this?!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri! Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii has to go!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, this is...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...Operation Arc-light!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:11.34,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Arc-light?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Mayu!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri! Wait, Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Secure the target!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Owowow...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:30.52,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this seriously happening in Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:33.73,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:34.90,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:12.69,0:19:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... the time machine’s.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they not make it in time?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:22.49,0:19:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:41.80,0:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri... Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:46.97,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 30,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s still incomplete.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:57.69,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:08.41,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I chose this world line because\NI thought it was the best choice!
Dialogue: 30,0:20:13.87,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This was the one and only\Nworld line built upon Kurisu’s sacrifice!
Dialogue: 30,0:20:19.59,0:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... And yet, why?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 30,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Okarin.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:37.69,0:20:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tutturu! It’s Mayushii!
Dialogue: 30,0:20:40.69,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I wanted to talk to you in person,\Nbut I didn’t know if could get it all out.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:46.57,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I was worried Okarin might\Ntry to stop me, so I’ll just say it here.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going with Suzu-san to the past.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:55.33,0:20:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll probably be upset and are wondering why.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:59.09,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this is something I have to do.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:03.38,0:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that day, I was the one who did it.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:07.18,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how bad things got,
Dialogue: 30,0:21:10.18,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,my strong, strong Hikoboshi would\Nget back up with a great big laugh.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:14.27,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I’m the one who hid him\Nbehind a bunch of dark clouds.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I think I was wrong.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:22.28,0:21:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone wasn’t pushing the\Nweight of the future solely on Okarin.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:28.03,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Steins Gate must be\Nsomething we all find together.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s at your side.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:34.54,0:21:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru-kun’s there, Suzu-san’s there...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:38.00,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...Luka-kun’s there,\NFaris-chan’s there, Yuki-san’s there...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...and even Maho-san’s there too.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:46.51,0:21:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So now it’s my turn.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:49.39,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, since I’m Lab Member 002,\Nthis’ll be my first very big mission!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:57.39,0:22:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure Okarin will be worried,\Nbut it’ll all be okay.
Dialogue: 30,0:22:01.48,0:22:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, even if something does happen,\NI know in my heart that you’ll come to save me.
Dialogue: 30,0:22:08.70,0:22:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hououin Kyouma I love so much will\Ncome swooping in on a brand-new time machine.
Dialogue: 30,0:22:15.91,0:22:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why I’ve decided to go.
Dialogue: 30,0:22:18.71,0:22:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I’ll come back,\Nso just wait for me, okay?
Dialogue: 30,0:22:25.17,0:22:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I... love Hououin Kyouma.
Dialogue: 30,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But, guess what?
Dialogue: 30,0:22:31.55,0:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Okabe Rintaro even more!
